nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: Animated CGI clip showing a diverse group of four characters inside a retro diner with a red and white checkered floor. In the foreground, a tall, shirtless man with prominent muscles has slid a young woman with dark hair and a leopard-print vest along the floor and slapped her against the bar, where she now leans back against his legs. In the mid-ground, another woman in a yellow jacket sits alone at a small table near a window, seemingly unperturbed as she eats a hamburger. Two figures, one a young man with a red hoodie and another man standing behind him, are seated on the right. The lighting is bright and stylized, shining in through the windows and highlighting the dramatic composition and the tense, observational mood among the characters.
